{"tid":1544062,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[垃圾黨鐵] 除左罷買可唔可以做多少少野","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:05:15.000Z","uid":207925,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"326b7be9b3385156073cfdf01b6c248fdd7ccf92","tid":1544062,"uid":207925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"其實都明白唔係個個都罷搭到 始終係好方便<br />\n但你搭時可唔可以做多少少<br />\n除左罷買港鐵期下商場外<br />\n跳閘唔敢 咪買<span style=\"color: green;\">綠卡</span>囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家跳閘嘅都係班後生 其實都係揸學生八達通<br />\n對黨鐵黎講冇左少少錢真係濕濕碎<br />\n但重點係揸成人八達通 月票嘅你地 <br />\n日日過海幾廿蚊 其實都係比港共食返<br />\n不如每程$1.9唔好助養港共 警犬好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n200萬人出過黎 周圍都係手足 有咩事大家保大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果大家都係過唔到心理關口<br />\n不如諗下<span style=\"color: red;\">血洗元朗 太子站</span>個刻你有幾嬲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家一齊做鳩黨鐵呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"}]}